data.description: Indulge in luxury with this 4-bed, 2-bath haven, recently remodeled to perfection. A split floor plan offers privacy, complemented by a brand-new kitchen and bathrooms, featuring 60-inch upper cabinets and soft-close drawers. Designer touches, new lighting, smart wall dimmers, and fresh paint create a serene, spa-like ambiance. Nestled on a corner lot, surrounded by wood preserves, mature trees, and a lush garden, this home seamlessly blends coastal calm with natural beauty. Enjoy outdoor living, all while being near shopping, dining, I-95, and the allure of Amelia Island. Welcome to your tranquil paradise.
